## About This Vlog

In this vlog, I share my learning journey during my Vinternship with VLED Lab.  
I explain what I learned, the challenges I faced, how I solved them, and how this internship helped me grow technically and conceptually.

This video is meant for students who are learning development concepts and want a realistic view of the learning process.

## What You Will Learn

- How I approached tasks during Vinternship  
- Key technical concepts I learned (Express, MVC, Repository Pattern, Dependency Injection)  
- Common mistakes I made and how I fixed them  
- Tips for beginners starting their Vinternship journey  

